<h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>

<p>We have now created two microservices and established communication between them.</p>

<p><img src="/images/Spring-Boot-Microservice-1-CCS-FS.png" alt="Image" title="Spring-Boot-Microservice-1-CCS-FS" /></p>

<p>However, we are hardcoding the url for FS in CCS. That means when new instances of FS are launched up we have no way to distribute load between them.</p>

<p>In the next part, we will enable client side load distribution using Ribbon.</p>

